[This disease is totally preventable through a vaccine. It is very
cheap insurance compared to losing your companion and your investment.
The fact of unvaccinated horses succumbing to the disease should cause
people to take extreme caution with mosquitoes as the disease can be
fatal to humans. - Mod.TG]

